# How to start 'security'?
The objective of this post, is to make easier to understand: what activities are recommended to enable your start-up application security. This article is going cover main areas like secure development lifecycle, choosen tools with implementations and even how to build foundation for seperate team and standarization.  
Disclaimer
JUST DO IT. Doing something, not necessary perfect or even good, is still better than NOT doing. Mastr yoda wouldn't be happy, but `trying` is our best, and only, option. There is no such a thing as perfected app security. 
